{{Databox}}'''Abaraz Mqqurn n Adrar''' (s [[Tutlayt Tafransist|tfransist]]: Stade Adrar, s [[Tutlayt Taɛṛabt|tɛrabt]]: ملعب أدرار) iga yan ubaraz n [[Takurt n uḍar|tkurt n uḍaṛ]] illan ɣ tmdint n [[Agadir]] ɣ [[Lmɣrib]]. Nnuṛẓmn iflwan n ubaraz ad ass n 11 uktubr 2013, iwala ubaraz ad i tamawast n tɛɛurma d tunnunt, d ar t tjiray SONARGES (Tamssurt tanamurt n usufɣ d uswuddu n ibarazn). Ar isnubg ubaraz ad akkʷ tmnyugart n trabbut n [[Talḥasant n Ugadir|Talḥasant n ugadir]].

== Amzruy ==
Tbda twuri n ubaraz mqqurn n Adrar ɣ ass n 4 n wayyur wis 6 n usggʷas n 2004 s yan atig ilkkmn s 860 id mlyun n ddrhm amɣribi. Ikka t inn yadlli ittuskar lblan bac ad ikmml lbni nns d ad yujad ɣ 2007, afad ad gis ittunḍam ukrwas n umaḍal ɣ Lmɣrib ɣ usggʷas n 2010. Zɣ ɣ akud ann a s ibda ttmwil n usɣnu ittubḍa f isggʷasn ar d ikmml lbni nns ɣ wayyur wis 8 n 2013. Zɣ ɣ akud ann a s ibda ubaraz ar isnubg d ar isbrrak tmnyugart n trabbut n [[Talḥasant n Ugadir|Talḥasant n ugadir]].

